sub_title: Sr. Product Owner at Liberty Global
summary: As an experienced international product leader specialized in user interfaces (UI) in a technology company I yearn to design and plan innovative products and services that users will love. To achieve this I continuously align expectations between internal stakeholders, customers, third-parties leading my team to handle shifting priorities. I'm very passionate with cloud services, IoT, big data and I like working in global, fast-paced companies where I can undertake a broad range of challenges on a daily basis.
